Riddle me this..  They must be manipulating because of the reverse messages
I get.  I spoke of this earlier in an email and I have attached an example.
Recently I did a session where I hear real-time &quot;GREAT BATTLE&quot; .  It
actually sounded like BABBLE but I recognized the word to mean battle
because a clip just before spoke of a soldier..  Anyway.. I reversed GREAT
BATTLE and the word BABBLE in reverse said WHO WON.  Now anyway you look at
it BATTLE or BABBLE in reverse when you or I say it will not come out as WHO
WON.  To verify this I recorded myself saying GREAT BATTLE and GREAT BABBLE
three time and lowering my voice each time.  I tried to match the intonation
of my clip as well.



I was correct.  When I say BATTLE or BABBLE it in no way sounds like &#39;Who
Won&#39;.  It isn&#39;t even decipherable. I have attached my clip from the session.
I saved it as GREAT BATTLE (f) WHO WON (r).  The next - Reverse Test - is me
saying GREAT BATTLE / BABBLE 3 times and then reversed.  



This happens all the time.  Spirit is using both sides of a digital
recording and that to me infers intelligence.


